#

Tuna Wrap with Lettuce and Tomato

10 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyWrap

Description

A simple yet satisfying wrap loaded with fresh ingredients and protein-rich tuna.

Ingredients

  • whole wheat tortilla: 1
  • canned tuna (drained): 1 can (5 oz)
  • lettuce (any variety): 1 cup
  • tomato (sliced): 1 medium
  • greek yogurt (as a spread): 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
